(13, 'Se7en', 'Thriller', 'David Fincher', 'Arnold Kopelson and Phyllis Carlyle', 'Andrew Kevin Walker', 'John Travolta, Uma Thurman, Samuel L. Jackson, and Bruce Willis', 'Two detectives, a rookie and a veteran, hunt a serial killer who uses the seven deadly sins as his motives.', 'September 15, 1995', '1670855252.jpg', '2022-12-12 06:27:32', '2022-12-12 06:27:32'),
(14, 'Sweet & Sour', 'Romance', 'Lee Gye-byeok', 'Park Se-joon', 'Kurumi Inui', 'Jang Ki-yong, Chae Soo-bin, and Krystal Jung', 'Faced with real-world opportunities and challenges, a couple endures the highs and lows of trying to make a long-distance relationship survive.', 'June 4, 2021', '1670855312.jpg', '2022-12-12 06:28:32', '2022-12-12 06:28:32'),
(15, 'The Girl With the Dragon Tattoo', 'Mystery', 'David Fincher', 'Scott Rudin, Ole Søndberg, , Søren Stærmose, and Ceán Chaffin', 'Stieg Larsson', 'Daniel Craig, Rooney Mara, Christopher Plummer, Stellan Skarsgård, Steven Berkoff, Robin Wright, Yorick van Wageningen, and Joely Richardson', 'Disgraced financial reporter Mikael Blomkvist (Daniel Craig) finds a chance to redeem his honor after being hired by wealthy Swedish industrialist Henrik Vanger (Christopher Plummer) to solve the 40-year-old murder of Vanger\'s niece, Harriet. Vanger believes that Harriet was killed by a member of his own family. Eventually joining Blomkvist on his dangerous quest for the truth is Lisbeth Salander (Rooney Mara), an unusual but ingenious investigator whose fragile trust is not easily won.', 'December 21, 2011', '1670855410.jpg', '2022-12-12 06:30:10', '2022-12-12 06:32:01'),
(16, 'The Nun', 'Horror', 'Corin Hardy', 'Peter Safran and James Wan', 'James Wan and Gary Dauberman', 'Demián Bichir, Taissa Farmiga, and Jonas Bloquet', 'When a young nun at a cloistered abbey in Romania takes her own life, a priest with a haunted past and a novitiate on the threshold of her final vows are sent by the Vatican to investigate. Together, they uncover the order\'s unholy secret. Risking not only their lives but their faith and their very souls, they confront a malevolent force in the form of a demonic nun.', 'September 7, 2018', '1670855594.jpg', '2022-12-12 06:33:14', '2022-12-12 06:33:14'),
(17, 'Dune', 'Adventure', 'Denis Villeneuve', 'Mary Parent, Denis Villeneuve, Cale Boyter, and Joe Caracciolo Jr.', 'Frank Herbert', 'Timothée Chalamet, Rebecca Ferguson, Oscar Isaac, Josh Brolin, Stellan Skarsgård, Dave Bautista, Stephen McKinley Henderson, Zendaya, Chang Chen, Charlotte Rampling, Jason Momoa, and Javier Bardem', 'Paul Atreides, a brilliant and gifted young man born into a great destiny beyond his understanding, must travel to the most dangerous planet in the universe to ensure the future of his family and his people. As malevolent forces explode into conflict over the planet\'s exclusive supply of the most precious resource in existence, only those who can conquer their own fear will survive.', 'October 22, 2021', '1670855699.jpg', '2022-12-12 06:34:59', '2022-12-12 06:34:59'),
(18, 'The Searchers', 'Western', 'John Ford', 'C.V. Whitney Pictures', 'Frank S. Nugent', 'John Wayne, Jeffrey Hunter, Vera Miles, and Ward Bond', 'An American Civil War veteran embarks on a years-long journey to rescue his niece from the Comanches after the rest of his brother\'s family is massacred in a raid on their Texas farm.', 'May 16, 1956', '1670855805.jpg', '2022-12-12 06:36:45', '2022-12-12 06:36:45'),
(19, 'Pulp Fiction', 'Drama', 'Quentin Tarantino', 'Lawrence Bender', 'Quentin Tarantino', 'John Travolta, Uma Thurman, Samuel L. Jackson, and Bruce Willis', 'The lives of two mob hitmen, a boxer, a gangster and his wife, and a pair of diner bandits intertwine in four tales of violence and redemption.', 'May 21, 1994', '1670855878.jpg', '2022-12-12 06:37:58', '2022-12-12 06:37:58'),
(20, 'The Godfather', 'Drama', 'Francis Ford Coppola', 'Albert S. Ruddy', 'Mario Puzo and Francis Ford Coppola', 'Marlon Brando, Al Pacino, James Caan, and Diane Keaton', 'The aging patriarch of an organized crime dynasty in postwar New York City transfers control of his clandestine empire to his reluctant youngest son.', 'March 14, 1972', '1670855923.jpg', '2022-12-12 06:38:43', '2022-12-12 06:38:43'),
(21, 'Groundhog Day', 'Comedy', 'Harold Ramis', 'Trevor Albert and Harold Ramis', 'Danny Rubin and Harold Ramis', 'Bill Murray, Andie MacDowell, Chris Elliott, and Stephen Tobolowsky', 'A narcissistic, self-centered weatherman finds himself in a time loop on Groundhog Day, and the day keeps repeating until he gets it right.', 'February 12, 1993', '1670855978.jpg', '2022-12-12 06:39:38', '2022-12-12 06:39:38'),
(22, 'Through My Window', 'Romance', 'Marçal Forès', 'Núria Valls and Adrián Guerra', 'Ariana Godoy', 'Julio Peña, Clara Galle, and Pilar Castro', 'Raquel has a longtime crush on her hot neighbour, Ares, whom she secretly watches but has never spoken to. Can she make Ares fall in love with her?', 'February 4, 2022', '1670856056.jpg', '2022-12-12 06:40:56', '2022-12-12 06:40:56'),
(23, 'After', 'Romance', 'Jenny Gage', 'Jennifer Gibgot, Courtney Solomon, Mark Canton, Aron Levitz, Anna Todd , Meadow Williams, and Dennis Pelino', 'Anna Todd', 'Josephine Langford, Hero Fiennes Tiffin, Selma Blair, Inanna Sarkis, Shane Paul McGhie, Pia Mia, Khadijha Red Thunder, Dylan Arnold, Samuel Larsen, Jennifer Beals, and Peter Gallagher', 'A young woman falls for a guy with a dark secret and the two embark on a rocky relationship. Based on the novel by Anna Todd.', 'April 12, 2019', '1670856147.jpg', '2022-12-12 06:42:27', '2022-12-12 06:42:27'),
(24, 'Before I Go to Sleep', 'Mystery', 'Rowan Joffé', 'Avi Lerner, Liza Marshall, Mark Gill, Matthew O\'Toole, and Ridley Scott', 'Rowan Joffé', 'Nicole Kidman, Mark Strong, Colin Firth, and Anne-Marie Duff', 'Ever since a vicious attack nearly claimed her life, Christine Lucas (Nicole Kidman) has suffered from anterograde amnesia and is unable to form new memories. Every morning, she becomes reacquainted with her husband, Ben (Colin Firth), and the other constants in her life. In accordance with her doctor\'s (Mark Strong) instructions, Christine keeps a video diary. As Christine starts to uncover terrifying truths about her past, she begins to question everything -- and everyone -- around her.', 'September 5, 2014', '1670856217.jpg', '2022-12-12 06:43:37', '2022-12-12 06:43:37'),
(25, 'Fullmetal Alchemist', 'Fantasy', 'Fumihiko Sori', 'Yumihiko Yoshihara', 'Hiromu Arakawa', 'Ryosuke Yamada, Tsubasa Honda, Dean Fujioka, Ryuta Sato, Jun Kunimura, Fumiyo Kohinata, Yasuko Matsuyuki', 'The Elric brothers’ long and winding journey comes to a close in this epic finale, where they must face off against an unworldly, nationwide threat.', 'September 24, 2022', '1670950689.jpg', '2022-12-13 09:58:09', '2022-12-13 09:58:55'),
(26, 'If I Stay', 'Romance', 'R. J. Cutler', 'Alison Greenspan', 'Gayle Forman', 'Chloë Grace Moretz, Mireille Enos, Joshua Leonard, Stacy Keach', 'Mia Hall (Chloë Grace Moretz), a talented young cellist, thought the most difficult decision she would ever have to make would be whether to pursue her musical dreams at prestigious Juilliard or follow her heart to be with the love of her life, Adam (Jamie Blackley), a rock singer/guitarist. However, a car wreck changes everything in an instant, and now Mia\'s life hangs in the balance. Suspended between life and death, Mia faces a choice that will decide her future.', 'August 18, 2014', '1670953619.jpg', '2022-12-13 10:46:59', '2022-12-13 10:46:59'),
(27, 'The Girl on the Train', 'Mystery', 'Tate Taylor', 'Marc Platt, Jared LeBoff', 'Paula Hawkins', 'Emily Blunt, Rebecca Ferguson, Haley Bennett, Justin Theroux, Luke Evans, Allison Janney', 'Commuter Rachel Watson (Emily Blunt) catches daily glimpses of a seemingly perfect couple, Scott and Megan, from the window of her train. One day, Watson witnesses something shocking unfold in the backyard of the strangers\' home. Rachel tells the authorities what she thinks she saw after learning that Megan is now missing and feared dead. Unable to trust her own memory, the troubled woman begins her own investigation, while police suspect that Rachel may have crossed a dangerous line.', 'October 7, 2016', '1670953799.jpg', '2022-12-13 10:49:59', '2022-12-13 10:50:26'),
(28, 'Eerie', 'Horror', 'Mikhail Red', 'Carlo Katigbak, Malou N. Santos, Olivia Lamasan, Abhi Rastogi, Gin Kai Chan, Justin Deimen', 'Mikhail Red, Rae Red, Mariah Reodica', 'Carlo Katigbak, Malou N. Santos, Olivia Lamasan, Abhi Rastogi, Gin Kai Chan, Justin Deimen', 'Eerie A guidance counsellor\'s special talents help her unravel the mystery behind the unexpected and gruesome death of a student at a Catholic school for girls.', 'March 27, 2019', '1670953952.jpg', '2022-12-13 10:52:32', '2022-12-13 10:52:32'),
(29, 'Mortal Kombat', 'Adventure', 'Simon McQuoid', 'James Wan, Todd Garner, Simon McQuoid, E. Bennett Walsh', 'Oren Uziel, Greg Russo', 'Lewis Tan, Jessica McNamee, Josh Lawson, Tadanobu Asano, Mehcad Brooks, Ludi Lin, Chin Han, Joe Taslim, Hiroyuki Sanada,', 'Hunted by the fearsome warrior Sub-Zero, MMA fighter Cole Young finds sanctuary at the temple of Lord Raiden. Training with experienced fighters Liu Kang, Kung Lao and the rogue mercenary Kano, Cole prepares to stand with Earth\'s greatest champions to take on the enemies from Outworld in a high-stakes battle for the universe.', 'April 23, 2021', '1670954108.jpg', '2022-12-13 10:55:08', '2022-12-13 10:55:08'),
(30, 'Three Thousand Years of Longing', 'Fantasy', 'Jon Watts', 'Kevin Feige, Amy Pascal', 'Chris McKenna, Erik Sommers', 'Tom Holland , Zendaya Benedict, Cumberbatch Jacob, Batalon Jon, Favreau Jamie, Foxx Willem, Dafoe Alfred, Molina Benedict, Wong Tony, Revolori Marisa, Tomei Andrew, Garfield Tobey Maguire', 'With Spider-Man\'s identity now revealed, our friendly neighborhood web-slinger is unmasked and no longer able to separate his normal life as Peter Parker from the high stakes of being a superhero. When Peter asks for help from Doctor Strange, the stakes become even more dangerous, forcing him to discover what it truly means to be Spider-Man.', 'December 17, 2021', '1670969363.jpg', '2022-12-13 15:09:23', '2022-12-13 15:09:23'),
(31, 'The Vow', 'Romance', 'Michael Sucsy', 'Roger Birnbaum, Gary Barber, Jonathan Glickman, Paul Taublieb', 'Stuart Sender', 'Rachel McAdams, Channing Tatum, Sam Neill, Scott Speedman, Jessica Lange, Jessica McNamee', 'Paige (Rachel McAdams) and Leo (Channing Tatum) are happily married newlyweds, but their idyllic life together suddenly shatters when a car accident leaves her in a coma. When Paige awakes, she has severe memory loss and doesn\'t know Leo. She also has a confusing relationship with her parents (Sam Neill, Jessica Lange) and still harbors feelings for a former fiance (Scott Speedman). Despite these difficult obstacles, Leo is determined to renew their bond and rebuild their marriage.', 'February 10, 2012', '1670969847.jpg', '2022-12-13 15:17:27', '2022-12-13 15:17:27'),
(32, 'Arrival', 'Mystery', 'Denis Villeneuve', 'Shawn Levy, Dan Levine, Aaron Ryder, David Linde', 'Ted Chiang', 'Amy Adams, Jeremy Renner, Forest Whitaker, Michael Stuhlbarg, Tzi Ma', 'Linguistics professor Louise Banks (Amy Adams) leads an elite team of investigators when gigantic spaceships touch down in 12 locations around the world. As nations teeter on the verge of global war, Banks and her crew must race against time to find a way to communicate with the extraterrestrial visitors. Hoping to unravel the mystery, she takes a chance that could threaten her life and quite possibly all of mankind.', 'November 11, 2016', '1670970204.jpg', '2022-12-13 15:23:24', '2022-12-13 15:23:24'),
(33, 'Army of the Dead', 'Horror', 'Louis Leterrier', 'Alex Kurtzman, Roberto Orci, Bobby Cohen', 'oaz Yakin, Edward Ricourt', 'Mark Ruffalo, Woody Harrelson, Mélanie Laurent, Isla Fisher, Dave Franco, Common Michael, Caine Morgan Freeman', 'Charismatic magician Atlas (Jesse Eisenberg) leads a team of talented illusionists called the Four Horsemen. Atlas and his comrades mesmerize audiences with a pair of amazing magic shows that drain the bank accounts of the corrupt and funnel the money to audience members. A federal agent (Mark Ruffalo) and an Interpol detective (Mélanie Laurent) intend to rein in the Horsemen before their next caper, and they turn to Thaddeus (Morgan Freeman), a famous debunker, for help.', 'May 31, 2013', '1670970453.jpg', '2022-12-13 15:27:33', '2022-12-13 15:27:33'),
(34, 'Spider-Man; No Way Home', 'Adventure', 'Jon Watts', 'Kevin Feige, Amy Pascal', 'Chris McKenna, Erik Sommers', 'Tom Holland, Zendaya, Benedict Cumberbatch, Jacob Batalon', 'With Spider-Man\'s identity now revealed, our friendly neighborhood web-slinger is unmasked and no longer able to separate his normal life as Peter Parker from the high stakes of being a superhero. When Peter asks for help from Doctor Strange, the stakes become even more dangerous, forcing him to discover what it truly means to be Spider-Man.', 'December 17, 2021', '1670970905.jpg', '2022-12-13 15:35:05', '2022-12-13 15:35:05'),
(35, 'Alienoid', 'Fantasy', 'Choi Dong-hoon', 'Ahn Soo-Hyun', 'Choi Dong-hoon', 'Ryu Jun-yeol, Kim Woo-bin, Kim Tae-ri, So Ji-sub, Yum Jung-ah', 'Gurus in the late Goryeo dynasty try to obtain a fabled, holy sword, and humans in 2022 hunt down an alien prisoner that is locked in a human\'s body. The two parties cross paths when a time-traveling portal opens up.', 'August 26, 2022', '1670971127.jpg', '2022-12-13 15:38:47', '2022-12-13 15:38:47'),
(36, 'All My Life', 'Romance', 'Marc Meyers', 'Todd Garner, Sean Robins', 'Todd Rosenberg', 'Jessica Rothe, Harry Shum Jr., Marielle Scott ,Kyle Allen, Jay Pharoah', 'Jennifer Carter and Solomon Chau are a sweet, fun-loving, newly engaged couple who are ready to start their lives together. But when Solomon is diagnosed with terminal liver cancer, their hopes for a summer wedding become impossible. With time running out, their friends and families soon devise an inspirational plan to help Jennifer and Solomon realize their dream wedding.', 'December 4, 2020', '1670971218.jpg', '2022-12-13 15:40:18', '2022-12-13 15:40:18'),
(37, 'Now You See Me', 'Mystery', 'Louis Leterrier', 'Alex Kurtzman, Roberto Orci, Bobby Cohen', 'Boaz Yakin, Edward Ricourt', 'Jesse Eisenberg, Mark Ruffalo, Woody Harrelso, Mélanie Laurent, Isla Fisher, Dave Franco', 'Charismatic magician Atlas (Jesse Eisenberg) leads a team of talented illusionists called the Four Horsemen. Atlas and his comrades mesmerize audiences with a pair of amazing magic shows that drain the bank accounts of the corrupt and funnel the money to audience members. A federal agent (Mark Ruffalo) and an Interpol detective (Mélanie Laurent) intend to rein in the Horsemen before their next caper, and they turn to Thaddeus (Morgan Freeman), a famous debunker, for help.', 'May 31, 2013', '1670971342.jpg', '2022-12-13 15:42:22', '2022-12-13 15:42:22'),
(38, 'The Devine Fury', 'Horror', 'Kim Joo-hwan', 'Park Ah-Hyeoung, Im Jeon-Hyeok', 'Kim Joo-hwan', 'Park Seo-joon Ahn, Sung-ki Woo, Do-hwan, Park Ji-hyun', 'After waking up with mysterious wounds on his hands, a champion MMA fighter finds himself in an otherworldly battle against evil forces wreaking havoc in the human world.', 'July 31, 2019', '1670971445.jpg', '2022-12-13 15:44:05', '2022-12-13 15:44:05'),
(39, 'F9', 'Adventure', 'Justin Lin', 'Neal H. Morit, Vin Diesel, Justin Lin, Jeffrey Kirschenbaum, Joe Roth, Clayton Townsend, Samantha Vincent', 'Justin Lin, Alfredo Botello, Daniel Casey', 'Vin Diesel, Michelle Rodriguez, Tyrese Gibson, Chris \"Ludacris\" Bridges, John Cena', 'Dom Toretto is living the quiet life off the grid with Letty and his son, but they know that danger always lurks just over the peaceful horizon. This time, that threat forces Dom to confront the sins of his past to save those he loves most. His crew soon comes together to stop a world-shattering plot by the most skilled assassin and high-performance driver they\'ve ever encountered -- Dom\'s forsaken brother.', 'June 25, 2021', '1670971842.jpg', '2022-12-13 15:50:42', '2022-12-13 15:50:42'),
(40, 'Glorious', 'Fantasy', 'Rebekah McKendry', 'Bob Portal, Inderpal Singh, Joe Wicker, Morgan Peter Brown, Jason Scott Goldberg, Christian Armogida', 'Todd Rigney', 'Ryan Kwanten, J. K. Simmons', 'After a breakup, Wes ends up at a remote rest stop. He finds himself locked inside the bathroom with a mysterious figure speaking from an adjacent stall. Soon Wes realizes he is involved in a situation more terrible than he could imagine.', 'August 18, 2022', '1670971924.jpg', '2022-12-13 15:52:04', '2022-12-13 15:52:04'),
(41, 'Five Feet Apart', 'Romance', 'Justin Baldoni', 'Cathy Schulman, Justin Baldoni, Christopher H. Warner', 'Mikki Daughtry, Tobias Iaconis', 'Haley Lu Richardson, Cole Sprouse', 'Seventeen-year-old Stella spends most of her time in the hospital as a cystic fibrosis patient. Her life is full of routines, boundaries and self-control -- all of which get put to the test when she meets Will, an impossibly charming teen who has the same illness. There\'s an instant flirtation, though restrictions dictate that they must maintain a safe distance between them. As their connection intensifies, so does the temptation to throw the rules out the window and embrace that attraction.', 'March 15, 2019', '1670972028.jpg', '2022-12-13 15:53:48', '2022-12-13 15:53:48'),
(42, 'I Still See You', 'Mystery', 'Scott Speer', 'Paul Brooks, Leon Clarance', 'Jason Fuchs', 'Bella Thorne, Richard Harmon, Dermot Mulroney', 'After a cataclysmic event leaves the world haunted by ghost-like spectres called `Remnants\', a high school student is stalked by an angry, violent Remnant who wants to kill her.', 'October 12, 2018', '1670972181.jpg', '2022-12-13 15:56:21', '2022-12-13 15:56:21'),
(43, 'Slender Man', 'Mystery', 'Mike Barker', 'Bruna Papandrea, Jeanne Snow, Erik Feig, Lucy Kitada, Mila Kunis', 'Jessica Knoll', 'Mila Kunis', 'A writer\'s perfectly crafted New York City life starts to unravel when a true-crime documentary forces her to confront her harrowing high school history and question the choices she made as a teenager.', 'October 7, 2022', '1670972288.jpg', '2022-12-13 15:58:08', '2022-12-13 15:58:08'),
(44, 'The Curse of La Llorona', 'Horror', 'Michael Chaves', 'James Wan, Gary Dauberman, Emile Gladstone', 'Mikki Daughtry, Tobias Iaconis', 'Linda Cardellini, Raymond Cruz, Patricia Velásquez', 'In 1970s Los Angeles, the legendary ghost La Llorona is stalking the night -- and the children. Ignoring the eerie warning of a troubled mother, a social worker and her own kids are drawn into a frightening supernatural realm. Their only hope of surviving La Llorona\'s deadly wrath is a disillusioned priest who practices mysticism to keep evil at bay.', 'April 19, 2019', '1670972387.jpg', '2022-12-13 15:59:47', '2022-12-13 15:59:47'),
(45, 'Bloodshot', 'Adventure', 'David S. F. Wilson', 'Neal H. Moritz, Toby Jaffe, Dinesh Shamdasani, Vin Diesel', 'Jeff Wadlow', 'Vin Diesel, Eiza González, Sam Heughan, Toby Kebbell, Guy Pearce', 'After he and his wife are murdered, marine Ray Garrison is resurrected by a team of scientists. Enhanced with nanotechnology, he becomes a superhuman, biotech killing machine - Bloodshot. As Ray first trains with fellow super-soldiers, he cannot recall anything from his former life. But when his memories flood back and he remembers the man that killed both him and his wife, he breaks out of the facility to get revenge, only to discover that there\'s more to the conspiracy than he thought.', 'March 13, 2020', '1670972478.jpg', '2022-12-13 16:01:18', '2022-12-13 16:01:18'),
(46, 'Thor: Love and Thunder', 'Fantasy', 'Taika Waititi', 'Taika Waititi', 'Taika Waititi, Jennifer Kaytin Robinson', 'Chris Hemsworth, Christian Bale, Tessa Thompson, Jaimie Alexander, Taika Waititi', 'After his retirement is interrupted by Gorr the God Butcher, a galactic killer who seeks the extinction of the gods, Thor Odinson enlists the help of King Valkyrie, Korg, and ex-girlfriend Jane Foster, who now wields Mjolnir as the Mighty Thor. Together they embark upon a harrowing cosmic adventure to uncover the mystery of the God Butcher’s vengeance and stop him before it’s too late.', 'July 8, 2022', '1670973431.jpg', '2022-12-13 16:17:11', '2022-12-13 16:17:11'),
(47, 'All Bright Places', 'Romance', 'Brett Haley', 'Paula Mazur, Mitchell Kaplan, Elle Fanning, Brittany Kahan-Ward, Doug Mankoff, Andrew Spaulding', 'Jennifer Niven', 'Elle Fanning, Justice Smith, Alexandra Shipp, Kelli O\'Hara, Lamar Johnson', 'After meeting each other, two teenagers struggle with the emotional and physical scars of their pasts. They discover that even the smallest moments can mean something.', 'February 28, 2020', '1670973520.jpg', '2022-12-13 16:18:40', '2022-12-13 16:18:40'),
(48, 'Recalled', 'Mystery', 'Seo Yoo-min', 'Jeong Hye-on', 'Seo Yoo-min', 'Seo Yea-ji Kim, Kang-woo', 'Sujin, who lost her memories due to a horrible incident, starts suspecting her husband. She is confused between reality and illusion, truth and lies.', 'April 21, 2021', '1670973596.jpg', '2022-12-13 16:19:56', '2022-12-13 16:19:56'),
(49, 'The Invisible Man', 'Horror', 'Leigh Whannell', 'Jason Blum, Kylie du Fresne', 'Leigh Whannell', 'Elisabeth Moss, Aldis Hodge, Storm Reid, Harriet Dyer', 'After staging his own suicide, a crazed scientist uses his power to become invisible to stalk and terrorize his ex-girlfriend. When the police refuse to believe her story, she decides to take matters into her own hands and fight back.', 'February 28, 2020', '1670973728.jpg', '2022-12-13 16:22:08', '2022-12-13 16:22:08'),
(50, 'The Batman', 'Adventure', 'Matt Reeves', 'Dylan Clark, Matt Reeves', 'Matt Reeves, Peter Craig', 'Robert Pattinson, Zoë Kravitz, Paul Dano, Jeffrey Wright, John Turturro', 'Batman ventures into Gotham City\'s underworld when a sadistic killer leaves behind a trail of cryptic clues. As the evidence begins to lead closer to home and the scale of the perpetrator\'s plans become clear, he must forge new relationships, unmask the culprit and bring justice to the abuse of power and corruption that has long plagued the metropolis.', 'March 4, 2022', '1670973853.jpg', '2022-12-13 16:24:13', '2022-12-13 16:24:13'),
(51, 'The Lost Girls', 'Fantasy', 'Livia De Paolis', 'Chris Curling, Meta Valentic, Sam Tipper-Hale, Peter Touche, Livia De Paolis', 'Livia De Paolis', 'Livia De Paolis, Ella-Rae Smith, Julian Ovenden, Parker Sawyers, Louis Partridge', 'The Lost Girls chronicles four generations of Darling women as they struggle in the aftermath of their adventures with Peter Pan (Louis Partridge) in Neverland. Like her grandmother (Vanessa Redgrave) and her mother Jane (Joely Richardson) before her, Wendy (Emily Carey and Livia De Paolis) must escape Pan’s hold on her and the promise he desperately wants her to keep. As her daughter Berry (Ella Rae-Smith) comes into Peter’s orbit, Wendy must fight to save her relationship with her daughter while reconciling her legacy.', 'June 17, 2022', '1670973977.jpg', '2022-12-13 16:26:17', '2022-12-13 16:26:17'),
(52, 'Titanic', 'Romance', 'James Cameron', 'James Cameron, Jon Landau', 'James Cameron', 'Leonardo DiCaprio, Kate Winslet, Billy Zane, Kathy Bates, Frances Fisher', 'James Cameron\'s \"Titanic\" is an epic, action-packed romance set against the ill-fated maiden voyage of the R.M.S. Titanic; the pride and joy of the White Star Line and, at the time, the largest moving object ever built. She was the most luxurious liner of her era -- the \"ship of dreams\" -- which ultimately carried over 1,500 people to their death in the ice cold waters of the North Atlantic in the early hours of April 15, 1912.', 'December 19, 1997', '1670974064.jpg', '2022-12-13 16:27:44', '2022-12-13 16:27:44'),
(53, 'Reminiscence', 'Mystery', 'Lisa Joy', 'Lisa Joy, Jonathan Nolan, Michael De Luca, Aaron Ryder', 'Lisa Joy', 'Hugh Jackman, Rebecca Ferguson, Thandiwe Newton, Cliff Curtis', 'Nick Bannister, a private investigator of the mind, navigates the darkly alluring world of the past by helping his clients access lost memories. Living on the fringes of the sunken Miami coast, his life is forever changed as he uncovers a violent conspiracy while trying to solve the mystery behind a client who disappeared.', 'August 20, 2021', '1670974209.jpg', '2022-12-13 16:30:09', '2022-12-13 16:30:09'),
(54, 'A Quiet Place', 'Horror', 'John Krasinski', 'Michael Bay, Andrew Form, Brad Fuller', 'Bryan Woods, Scott Beck', 'Emily Blunt, John Krasinski', 'If they hear you, they hunt you. A family must live in silence to avoid mysterious creatures that hunt by sound. Knowing that even the slightest whisper or footstep can bring death, Evelyn and Lee are determined to find a way to protect their children while desperately searching for a way to fight back.', 'April 6, 2018', '1670974278.jpg', '2022-12-13 16:31:18', '2022-12-13 16:31:18'),
(55, 'The Great Wall', 'Adventure', 'Zhang Yimou', 'Thomas Tull, Charles Roven, Jon Jashni, Peter Loehr', 'Max Brooks, Edward Zwick, Marshall Herskovitz', 'Matt Damon, Jing Tian, Pedro Pascal, Willem Dafoe, Andy Lau', 'When a mercenary warrior (Matt Damon) is imprisoned within the Great Wall, he discovers the mystery behind one of the greatest wonders of the world. As wave after wave of marauding beasts besiege the massive structure, his quest for fortune turns into a journey toward heroism as he joins a huge army of elite warriors to confront the unimaginable and seemingly unstoppable force.', 'February 17, 2017', '1670974370.jpg', '2022-12-13 16:32:50', '2022-12-13 16:32:50'),
(56, 'Morbius', 'Fantasy', 'Daniel Espinosa', 'Avi Arad, Matt Tolmach, Lucas Foster', 'Matt Sazama, 	Burk Sharpless', 'Jared Leto, Matt Smith, Adria Arjona, Jared Harris, Al Madrigal', 'One of the most compelling and conflicted characters in Sony Pictures Universe of Marvel Characters comes to the big screen as Oscar® winner Jared Leto transforms into the enigmatic antihero Michael Morbius. Dangerously ill with a rare blood disorder and determined to save others suffering his same fate, Dr. Morbius attempts a desperate gamble. While at first it seems to be a radical success, a darkness inside him is unleashed. Will good override evil – or will Morbius succumb to his mysterious new urges?', 'April 1, 2022', '1670974470.jpg', '2022-12-13 16:34:30', '2022-12-13 16:34:30'),
(57, 'The Handmaiden', 'Romance', 'Park Chan-wook', 'Park Chan-wook, Syd Lim', 'Park Chan-wook, Jeong Seo-kyeong', 'Kim Min-hee, Kim Tae-ri, Ha Jung-woo, Cho Jin-woong', 'With help from an orphaned pickpocket (Kim Tae-ri), a Korean con man (Ha Jung-woo) devises an elaborate plot to seduce and bilk a Japanese woman (Kim Min-hee) out of her inheritance.', 'June 1, 2016', '1670974576.jpg', '2022-12-13 16:36:16', '2022-12-13 16:36:16'),
(58, 'Calls', 'Mystery', 'J. Sabarish', 'S. Jayakumar', 'J. Sabarish', 'V. J. Chitra, Vinodhini Devadarshini, R. Sundarrajan', 'Told through a series of interconnected phone conversations, these conversations chronicle the mysterious story of a group of strangers whose lives are thrown into disarray in the lead-up to an apocalyptic event.', 'February 26, 2002', '1670974723.jpg', '2022-12-13 16:38:43', '2022-12-13 16:38:43'),
(59, 'Halloween Kills', 'Horror', 'David Gordon Green', 'Malek Akkad, Jason Blum, Bill Block', 'Scott Teems, Danny McBride, David Gordon Green', 'Jamie Lee Curtis, Judy Greer, Andi Matichak, Will Patton, Thomas Mann', 'The nightmare isn\'t over as unstoppable killer Michael Myers escapes from Laurie Strode\'s trap to continue his ritual bloodbath. Injured and taken to the hospital, Laurie reunites with Tommy Doyle, the boy she was babysitting on the night Michael began his reign of terror. As Laurie continues to fight through the pain, Tommy leads an angry mob of vigilantes to rise up against Myers and destroy the evil once and for all.', 'October 15, 2022', '1670974844.jpg', '2022-12-13 16:40:44', '2022-12-13 16:40:44'),
(60, 'Pan', 'Adventure', 'Joe Wright', 'Greg Berlanti, Sarah Schechter, Paul Webster', 'Jason Fuchs', 'Hugh Jackman, Garrett Hedlund, Rooney Mara, Levi Miller, Amanda Seyfried', 'Living a bleak existence at a London orphanage, 12-year-old Peter (Levi Miller) finds himself whisked away to the fantastical world of Neverland. Adventure awaits as he meets new friend James Hook (Garrett Hedlund) and the warrior Tiger Lily (Rooney Mara). They must band together to save Neverland from the ruthless pirate Blackbeard (Hugh Jackman). Along the way, the rebellious and mischievous boy discovers his true destiny, becoming the hero forever known as Peter Pan.', 'October 9, 2015', '1670974953.jpg', '2022-12-13 16:42:33', '2022-12-13 16:42:33'),
(61, 'Fistful of Vengeance', 'Fantasy', 'Roel Reiné', 'Doug Mitchell, George Miller', 'Cameron Litvack, Jessica Chou, Yalun Tu', 'Iko Uwais, Lewis Tan, Lawrence Kao, Pearl Thusi, Francesca Corney', 'A revenge mission becomes a fight to save the world from an ancient threat when superpowered assassin Kai tracks a killer to Bangkok.', 'February 17, 2022', '1670975135.jpg', '2022-12-13 16:45:35', '2022-12-13 16:45:35'),
(62, 'Eternal Sunshine of the Spotless Mind', 'Romance', 'Michel Gondry', 'Steve Golin, Anthony Bregman', 'Charlie Kaufman, Michel Gondry, Pierre Bismuth', 'Jim Carrey, Kate Winslet, Kirsten Dunst, Mark Ruffalo', 'After a painful breakup, Clementine (Kate Winslet) undergoes a procedure to erase memories of her former boyfriend Joel (Jim Carrey) from her mind. When Joel discovers that Clementine is going to extremes to forget their relationship, he undergoes the same procedure and slowly begins to forget the woman that he loved. Directed by former music video director Michel Gondry, the visually arresting film explores the intricacy of relationships and the pain of loss.', 'March 19, 2004', '1670975254.jpg', '2022-12-13 16:47:34', '2022-12-13 16:47:34'),
(63, 'Enola Holmes', 'Mystery', 'Harry Bradbeer', 'Mary Parent, Alex Garcia, Ali Mendes, Millie Bobby Brown, Paige Brown', 'Nancy Springer', 'Millie Bobby, Brown Sam, Claflin Henry, Cavill Helena, Bonham Carter', 'While searching for her missing mother, intrepid teen Enola Holmes uses her sleuthing skills to outsmart big brother Sherlock and help a runaway lord.', 'September 23, 2020', '1670975395.jpg', '2022-12-13 16:49:55', '2022-12-13 16:49:55'),
(64, 'Us', 'Horror', 'Jordan Peele', 'Jason Blum, Ian Cooper, Sean McKittrick, Jordan Peele', 'Jordan Peele', 'Lupita Nyong\'o, Winston Duke, Elisabeth Moss, Tim Heidecker', 'Accompanied by her husband, son and daughter, Adelaide Wilson returns to the beachfront home where she grew up as a child. Haunted by a traumatic experience from the past, Adelaide grows increasingly concerned that something bad is going to happen. Her worst fears soon become a reality when four masked strangers descend upon the house, forcing the Wilsons into a fight for survival. When the masks come off, the family is horrified to learn that each attacker takes the appearance of one of them.', 'March 22, 2019', '1670975470.jpg', '2022-12-13 16:51:10', '2022-12-13 16:51:10'),
(65, 'Godzilla vs. Kong', 'Adventure', 'Adam Wingard', 'Thomas Tull, Jon Jashni, Brian Rogers, Mary Parent, Alex Garcia, Eric McLeod', 'Terry Rossio, Michael Dougherty, Zach Shields', 'Alexander Skarsgård, Millie Bobby, Brown Rebecca, Hall Brian, Tyree Henry', 'Kong and his protectors undertake a perilous journey to find his true home. Along for the ride is Jia, an orphaned girl who has a unique and powerful bond with the mighty beast. However, they soon find themselves in the path of an enraged Godzilla as he cuts a swath of destruction across the globe. The initial confrontation between the two titans -- instigated by unseen forces -- is only the beginning of the mystery that lies deep within the core of the planet.', 'March 31, 2021', '1670975560.jpg', '2022-12-13 16:52:40', '2022-12-13 16:52:40'),
(66, 'Wendell & Wild', 'Fantasy', 'Henry Selick', 'Henry Selick, Ellen Goldsmith-Vein, Jordan Peele, Win Rosenfeld', 'Henry Selick, Clay McLeod Chapman', 'Keegan-Michael Key, Jordan Peele, Angela Bassett, Lyric Ross', 'Two demon brothers enlist the aid of Kat Elliot — a tough teen with a load of guilt — to summon them to the Land of the Living. But what Kat demands in return leads to a brilliantly bizarre and comedic adventure like no other.', 'October 28, 2022', '1670975712.jpg', '2022-12-13 16:55:12', '2022-12-13 16:55:12'),
(67, 'To All the Boys I\'ve Loved Before', 'Romance', 'Susan Johnson', 'Jordan Levin, Matthew Kaplan, Dougie Cash', 'Sofia Alvarez', 'Lana Condor, Noah Centineo, Janel Parrish, Anna Cathcart, Andrew Bachelor', 'To All the Boys is a franchise consisting of American teenage romance installments, including three feature films and a spin-off television series, based on the titular trilogy of novels written by Jenny Han.', 'August 17, 2018', '1670975851.jpg', '2022-12-13 16:57:31', '2022-12-13 16:57:31'),
(68, 'Dobaaraa', 'Mystery', 'Anurag Kashyap', 'Shobha Kapoor, Ekta Kapoor, Sunit Khetrapal, Gaurav Bose', 'Oriol Paulo', 'Taapsee Pannu, Pavail Gulati', 'In the middle of a mysterious thunderstorm, a mother saves someone\'s life, which has unexpected consequences.', 'August 19, 2022', '1670975931.jpg', '2022-12-13 16:58:51', '2022-12-13 16:58:51'),
(69, 'The Conjuring', 'Horror', 'James Wan', 'Tony DeRosa-Grund, Peter Safran, Rob Cowan', 'Chad Hayes, Carey W. Hayes', 'Vera Farmiga, Patrick Wilson, Ron Livingston, Lili Taylor', 'In 1970, paranormal investigators and demonologists Lorraine (Vera Farmiga) and Ed (Patrick Wilson) Warren are summoned to the home of Carolyn (Lili Taylor) and Roger (Ron Livingston) Perron. The Perrons and their five daughters have recently moved into a secluded farmhouse, where a supernatural presence has made itself known. Though the manifestations are relatively benign at first, events soon escalate in horrifying fashion, especially after the Warrens discover the house\'s macabre history.', 'July 15, 2013', '1670976014.jpg', '2022-12-13 17:00:14', '2022-12-13 17:00:14'),
(70, 'Gods of Egypt', 'Adventure', 'Alex Proyas', 'Basil Iwanyk, Alex Proyas', 'Matt Sazama, Burk Sharpless', 'Nikolaj Coster-Waldau, Brenton Thwaites, Chadwick Boseman, Élodie Yung', 'The survival of mankind hangs in the balance when Set (Gerard Butler), the merciless god of darkness, usurps Egypt\'s throne and plunges the prosperous empire into chaos and conflict. Hoping to save the world and rescue his true love, a defiant mortal named Bek (Brenton Thwaites) forms an unlikely alliance with the powerful god Horus (Nikolaj Coster-Waldau). Their battle against Set and his henchmen takes them into the afterlife and across the heavens for an epic confrontation.', 'February 26, 2016', '1670976103.jpg', '2022-12-13 17:01:43', '2022-12-13 17:01:43'),
(71, 'Mortal Kombat Legends: Snow Blind (2022)', 'Fantasy', 'Ethan Spaulding', 'Rick Morales, Jim Krieg', 'Ed Boon, John Tobias', 'Jordan Rodrigues, Joel McHale, Jennifer Carpenter, Patrick Seitz', 'Hellbent on taking over Earthrealm, Kano viciously attacks town after town with the aid of three cold-blooded Black Dragon mercenaries. Those who don’t submit are annihilated but one young man won’t bend the knee to Kano: Kenshi.', 'October 9, 2022', '1670976206.jpg', '2022-12-13 17:03:26', '2022-12-13 17:03:26'),
(72, 'Single All The Way', 'Romance', 'Michael Mayer', 'Joel S. Rice', 'Chad Hodge', 'Michael Urie, Philemon Chambers, Luke Macfarlane, Barry Bostwick', 'Desperate to avoid his family\'s judgment about being single, Peter persuades best friend Nick to pose as his boyfriend on a trip home for the holidays', 'December 2, 2021', '1670976307.jpg', '2022-12-13 17:05:07', '2022-12-13 17:05:07'),
(73, 'Fever Dream', 'Mystery', 'Claudia Llosa', 'Mark Johnson, Tom Williams, Claudia Llosa', 'Samanta Schweblin', 'María Valverde, Dolores Fonzi', 'A young woman lies dying far from home. A boy sits beside her. She is not his mother. He is not her child. Together, they tell a haunting story of broken souls, an invisible threat and the power and desperation of family. Based on the internationally critically acclaimed homonymous novel by Samanta Schweblin.', 'October 6, 2021', '1670976393.jpg', '2022-12-13 17:06:33', '2022-12-13 17:06:33'),
(74, 'No One Gets Out Alive', 'Horror', 'Santiago Menghini', 'Jonathan Cavendish, Will Tennant', 'Jon Croker', 'Cristina Rodlo Marc Menchaca', 'Desperate and without documentation, a woman from Mexico moves into a rundown Cleveland boarding house. Then the unsettling cries and eerie visions begin.', 'September 29, 2021', '1670976578.jpg', '2022-12-13 17:09:38', '2022-12-13 17:09:38'),
(75, 'Divergent', 'Adventure', 'Neil Burger', 'Douglas Wick, Lucy Fisher, Pouya Shahbazian', 'Veronica Roth', 'Shailene Woodley, Theo James, Ashley Judd', 'Tris Prior (Shailene Woodley) lives in a futuristic world in which society is divided into five factions. As each person enters adulthood, he or she must choose a faction and commit to it for life. Tris chooses Dauntless -- those who pursue bravery above all else. However, her initiation leads to the discovery that she is a Divergent and will never be able to fit into just one faction. Warned that she must conceal her status, Tris uncovers a looming war which threatens everyone she loves.', 'March 21, 2014', '1670976667.jpg', '2022-12-13 17:11:07', '2022-12-13 17:11:07'),
(76, 'The King\'s Daughter', 'Fantasy', 'Sean McNamara', 'James Pang Hong, Paul Currie, Wei Han, Sean McNamara, David Brookwell, Hong Pang, Evan Wang, Qingfeng Du', 'Barry Berman, James Schamus', 'Pierce Brosnan, Kaya Scodelario, Benjamin Walker, William Hurt, Rachel Griffiths', 'King Louis XIV\'s quest for immortality leads him to capture and steal a mermaid\'s life force, a move that is further complicated by his illegitimate daughter\'s discovery of the creature.', 'January 21, 2022', '1670976967.jpg', '2022-12-13 17:16:07', '2022-12-13 17:16:07'),
(77, 'Crazy, Stupid, Love', 'Romance', 'Glenn Ficarra, John Requa', 'Steve Carell, Denise Di Novi', 'Dan Fogelman', 'Steve Carell, Ryan Gosling, Julianne Moore, Emma Stone', 'Cal Weaver (Steve Carell) is living the American dream. He has a good job, a beautiful house, great children and a beautiful wife, named Emily (Julianne Moore). Cal\'s seemingly perfect life unravels, however, when he learns that Emily has been unfaithful and wants a divorce. Over 40 and suddenly single, Cal is adrift in the fickle world of dating. Enter, Jacob Palmer (Ryan Gosling), a self-styled player who takes Cal under his wing and teaches him how to be a hit with the ladies.', 'July 29, 2011', '1670977091.jpg', '2022-12-13 17:18:11', '2022-12-13 17:18:11'),
(78, 'The 8th Night', 'Horror', 'Kim Tae-hyoung', 'Hyun Kwang Seo', 'Kim Tae-hyoung', 'Lee Sung-min, Park Hae-joon, Kim Yoo-jung, Nam Da-reum', 'With prayer beads in one hand and an axe in the other, a monk hunts down a millennia-old spirit that\'s possessing humans and unleashing hell on Earth.', 'July 2, 2021', '1670977235.jpg', '2022-12-13 17:20:35', '2022-12-13 17:20:35'),
(79, 'Oblivion', 'Adventure', 'Joseph Kosinski', 'Peter Chernin, Dylan Clark, Duncan Henderson, Joseph Kosinski, Barry Levine', 'Joseph Kosinski', 'Tom Cruise, Morgan Freeman, Olga Kurylenko', 'In the year 2077, Jack Harper (Tom Cruise) works as a security repairman on an Earth left empty and devastated after a war with aliens. Jack has two weeks left before his mission ends and he joins his fellow survivors on a faraway colony. However, Jack\'s concept of reality comes crashing down after he rescues a beautiful stranger (Olga Kurylenko) from a downed spacecraft. The woman\'s arrival triggers a chain of events that culminates in Jack\'s nearly single-handed battle to save mankind.', 'April 19, 2013', '1670977392.jpg', '2022-12-13 17:23:12', '2022-12-13 17:23:12'),
(80, 'Logan', 'Action', 'James Mangold', 'Hutch Parker Simon Kinberg Lauren Shuler Donner', 'Scott Frank James Mangold Michael Green', 'Hugh Jackman, Patrick Stewart, Dafne Keen, Boyd Holbrook', 'In a future where mutants are nearly extinct, an elderly and weary Logan leads a quiet life. But when Laura, a mutant child pursued by scientists, comes to him for help, he must get her to safety.', 'February 17, 2017', '1671020625.jpg', '2022-12-14 04:23:45', '2022-12-14 04:23:45'),
(81, 'Friday', 'Comedy', 'F. Gary Gray', 'Patricia Charbonnet', 'Ice Cube DJ Pooh', 'Ice Cube, Chris Tucker, Nia Long, Tom Lister Jr.', 'It\'s Friday, and Craig and Smokey must come up with $200 they owe a local bully or there won\'t be a Saturday.', 'April 26, 1995', '1671021225.jpg', '2022-12-14 04:33:45', '2022-12-14 04:33:45'),
(82, 'Go Now', 'Drama', 'Michael Winterbottom', 'PolyGram Filmed Entertainment BBC', 'Jimmy McGovern Paul Henry Powell', 'Robert Carlyle, Juliet Aubrey, James Nesbitt, Sophie Okonedo', 'Nick, is a young Scottish soccer player living in the big city. He meets Karen, and the two fall in love and move in together. Soon after, Nick exhibits signs of serious illness.', '16 September 1995', '1671021388.jpg', '2022-12-14 04:36:28', '2022-12-14 04:36:28'),
(83, 'Fallen', 'Thriller', 'Gregory Hoblit', 'Charles Roven Dawn Steel', 'Nicholas Kazan', 'Denzel Washington, John Goodman, Donald Sutherland, Embeth Davidtz', 'Homicide detective John Hobbes witnesses the execution of serial killer Edgar Reese. Soon after the execution, the killings start again, and they are very similar to Reese\'s style..', 'January 16, 1998', '1671021537.jpg', '2022-12-14 04:38:57', '2022-12-14 04:38:57'),
